<TEXT>
<P>
Speaking of cheap shots, why does Mike Downey require a full column to slam 
Margaret Court's sense of values? In a society that tends to dismiss people 
with strong convictions as bigoted fanatics, I find Margaret Court's comments 
to be a rare expression of great courage, integrity and dignity that are the 
