<P>
EARTHQUAKES -- PHILIPPINES; HELICOPTER ACCIDENTS -- PHILIPPINES; HELICOPTER 
ACCIDENTS -- MARINE CORPS (U.S.); PHILIPPINES -- RELIEF; DISASTERS -- 
PHILIPPINES; DISASTER RELIEF; CASUALTIES; RELIEF ORGANIZATIONS 
</P>
