<P>
Boeing Co. May Sell Canadian Unit: The Seattle-based firm, which has never been 
content with its de Havilland commuter aircraft division, said it is discussing 
selling Boeing Canada's de Havilland division to Aeritalia of Italy and 
Aerospatiale of France. 
