<P>
AUTOMOBILE INDUSTRY -- LABOR RELATIONS; AUTOMOBILE INDUSTRY -- UNITED STATES; 
CHRYSLER CORP; UNITED AUTO WORKERS; EMPLOYEE OWNED BUSINESS 
</P>
